query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `auditLogs` (
  `id` INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  `userId` INT NOT NULL,
  `action` VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
  `entityType` VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  `entityId` INT,
  `details` TEXT,
  `ipAddress` VARCHAR(45),
  `userAgent` TEXT,
  `createdAt` TIMESTAMP NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  INDEX `user_idx` (`userId`),
  INDEX `action_idx` (`action`),
  INDEX `entity_type_idx` (`entityType`),
  INDEX `created_at_idx` (`createdAt`)
);

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `projectClientAccess` (
  `id` INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  `projectId` INT NOT NULL,
  `clientUserId` INT NOT NULL,
  `accessLevel` ENUM('view', 'comment', 'upload') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'view',
  `grantedById` INT NOT NULL,
  `grantedAt` TIMESTAMP NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `revokedAt` TIMESTAMP NULL,
  INDEX `project_idx` (`projectId`),
  INDEX `client_idx` (`clientUserId`)
);
